*Anjin Miura, an honorific name given to the sailor William Adams (1564-1620)
*The name given to the character Blackthorne in James Clavell&#x27;s 1975 novel &quot;Shōgun&quot;
** &quot;Anjin&quot; (&quot;Shōgun&quot;), the first episode of the 2024 miniseries adapted from the book</text><links>
